file: tmp_【#わための誕生日2021】３Ｄお誕生日パーティー！！！【角巻わため⧸ホロライブ４期生】 [UHLdoq-T-mA]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_004.mov

scenes.description: Performance of 'Happy Synthesizer' by Watame and Haachama in a flower field.
MC section after the song. Watame and Haachama are joined by Botan to take some commemorative photos.

subtitles.english: I'll play a melody that'll wipe away your tears

subtitles.english: You don't have to try so hard to be strong, you know?

subtitles.english: It's fine to just be honest with yourself

subtitles.original: 消してあげるから　この音で
subtitles.english: I'll erase them all with this sound

subtitles.original: イエーイ！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: イエーイ！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: 楽しかったねー！
subtitles.english: That was fun!

subtitles.original: 楽しかったー！
subtitles.english: So much fun!

subtitles.original: イエーイ！
subtitles.english: Yay!

subtitles.original: あ、ただいまー。
subtitles.english: Ah, I'm back.

subtitles.original: あ、おかえりー。
subtitles.english: Ah, welcome back.

subtitles.original: あれ？ぼたんちゃん？
subtitles.english: Wait, Botan-chan?

subtitles.original: どうしてこの場所に…？
subtitles.english: How did you find this place...?

subtitles.original: 匂いでなんか分かっちゃった。
subtitles.english: I kind of figured it out by the smell.

subtitles.original: 匂いで分かっちゃった！？
subtitles.english: By the smell!?

subtitles.original: 匂いで分かっちゃった。え、これわための地元？
subtitles.english: By the smell. Is this Watame's hometown?

subtitles.original: そうだよ！あ、やべ、バレた！
subtitles.english: That's right! Oh no, I've been found!

subtitles.original: また遊びに来るよ。
subtitles.english: I'll come visit again.

subtitles.original: バレたバレたー！
subtitles.english: I've been found out!

subtitles.original: 生息地がバレたー！
subtitles.english: My habitat has been discovered!

subtitles.original: また遊びに来ちゃおうかなー。
subtitles.english: Maybe I'll come visit again.

subtitles.original: 狙われてるよー、わためー。
subtitles.english: You're being targeted, Watame.

subtitles.original: タレ持ってきたよ。
subtitles.english: I brought some dipping sauce.

subtitles.original: はあちゃまも後でタレ渡すね。
subtitles.english: Haachama, I'll give you some sauce later too.

subtitles.original: オッケー、オッケー。
subtitles.english: Okay, okay.

subtitles.original: じゃあさ、今日が最後になるかもしれないからさ…
subtitles.english: Well, since today might be the last time...

subtitles.original: 記念撮影しとく？
subtitles.english: Shall we take a commemorative photo?

subtitles.original: 撮っとく？いいかな？
subtitles.english: Shall we? Is that okay?

subtitles.original: しようか。
subtitles.english: Let's do it.

subtitles.original: スクショタイムってやつしてもいいかな？
subtitles.english: Can we have a screenshot time?

subtitles.original: あ、いいですよ。
subtitles.english: Oh, sure.

subtitles.original: じゃあ、３人でまず…
subtitles.english: Okay, the three of us first...

subtitles.original: 撮る？どんなポーズがいい？
subtitles.english: Take it? What kind of pose should we do?

subtitles.original: どうする？なんかコメントとかでも…
subtitles.english: What should we do? Maybe from the comments...

subtitles.original: そうね、コメント見たいポーズとかあったらぜひ。
subtitles.english: Right, if there are any poses you want to see, let us know in the comments.

subtitles.original: 何がいい？
subtitles.english: What would be good?

subtitles.original: 何がいい？草しかねえ！
subtitles.english: What would be good? There's nothing but 'Kusa' (grass)!

subtitles.original: 「草」のポーズ！？
subtitles.english: The 'Kusa' pose!?

subtitles.original: 「草」のポーズ！そのポーズ！
subtitles.english: The 'Kusa' pose! That pose!

subtitles.original: 草、草、わさ、わさ…
subtitles.english: Kusa, kusa, rustle, rustle...

subtitles.original: なんだこれ。
subtitles.english: What is this?

subtitles.original: せっかく集まったのに「草」のポーズ！
subtitles.english: We finally got together and we're doing the 'Kusa' pose!

subtitles.original: 「草」のポーズ！いい？
subtitles.english: The 'Kusa' pose! Is this okay?

subtitles.original: なんかある？
subtitles.english: Anything else?

subtitles.original: ある？わため先輩、なんかあります？撮りたいやつ。
subtitles.english: Is there? Watame-senpai, is there anything you want to take?

subtitles.original: つのドリル！
subtitles.english: Tsuno Drill (Horn Drill)!

subtitles.original: つのドリル！食らってよ、つのドリル！
subtitles.english: Tsuno Drill! Take this, Tsuno Drill!

subtitles.original: あ、いいよ。
subtitles.english: Oh, sure.

subtitles.original: 「うわあー」って言って！
subtitles.english: Say 'Whoaaa'!

subtitles.original: うわあー！待って待って！まだやってないって！
subtitles.english: Whoaaa! Wait, wait! I haven't done it yet!

subtitles.original: 行くよー！
subtitles.english: Here I go!

subtitles.original: はい！
subtitles.english: Yes!

subtitles.original: つのドリル！
subtitles.english: Tsuno Drill!

subtitles.original: したたたたたたー！
subtitles.english: Shtatatatata!

subtitles.original: 痛快、痛快！
subtitles.english: Refreshing, refreshing!

subtitles.original: 痛快、痛快！これ気持ちいいー。
subtitles.english: Refreshing, refreshing! This feels good.

subtitles.original: これでいいの！？
subtitles.english: Is this really okay!?

subtitles.original: いいのか？決まったー。
subtitles.english: Is it? It's decided.

subtitles.original: ちょっと！やめてー！
subtitles.english: Hey! Stop it!

subtitles.original: 地元でいいのか、こんな喧嘩して！
subtitles.english: Is it okay to fight like this in your hometown!

subtitles.original: やっちまおうぜー！
subtitles.english: Let's do it!

subtitles.original: うわあー！おらおらおらおらー！やべえ！食べられるー！
subtitles.english: Whoaaa! Ora ora ora ora! Oh no! I'm gonna be eaten!

subtitles.original: このままハート作ろうぜ。
subtitles.english: Let's make a heart like this.

subtitles.original: あ、いいよ！
subtitles.english: Oh, sure!

subtitles.original: ハート作ろう。命大事に。
subtitles.english: Let's make a heart. Treasure your life.

subtitles.original: 命大事に。なんか回復してきた。
subtitles.english: Treasure your life. I feel like I'm recovering.

subtitles.original: あ、本当？よかったよかった。
subtitles.english: Oh, really? That's good.

subtitles.original: ＨＰ、イエーイ！
subtitles.english: HP, yay!

subtitles.original: よしよしよしよし、いいぞ。回復してきた。ひでえ、ひでえな。
subtitles.english: Good, good, good. I'm recovering. That's terrible.

subtitles.original: ツーショットとか撮る？
subtitles.english: Shall we take some two-shots?

subtitles.original: あ、じゃあツーショット撮る。私あれするよ、カメラマンするよ。
subtitles.english: Oh, then let's take two-shots. I'll be the photographer.

subtitles.original: お、ししろカメラマン！
subtitles.english: Oh, Shishiro the photographer!

subtitles.original: ししろカメラマンにお願いしますよ！
subtitles.english: We're counting on you, Photographer Shishiro!

subtitles.original: ししろカメラマン、下から行く派だけどいいかな？
subtitles.english: Photographer Shishiro likes to shoot from below, is that okay?

subtitles.original: 何！？ローアングルだと！？
subtitles.english: What!? A low angle!?

subtitles.original: ししろカメラマンは下から…
subtitles.english: Photographer Shishiro from below...

subtitles.original: いやーん！何ー！？下から撮らないでー！
subtitles.english: Nooo! What!? Don't shoot from below!

subtitles.original: 下から行くよー！
subtitles.english: Going from below!

subtitles.original: いやーん！見ちゃダメー！
subtitles.english: Nooo! Don't look!

subtitles.original: 見せんな、見せんな！うわあー！やめてくださーい！
subtitles.english: Don't show it, don't show it! Whoaaa! Please stop!
